              </quote> and inserting
			 <quote>For purposes of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:203/ss:c/p:2,3,4" proposed="true">paragraphs (1), (2), and (3)</cato:entity-ref>
              </quote>; and</text>
					</subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="H8FC6A7878F4C48F9B25F7D5DC38B29D1">
            <enum>(D)</enum>
            <text>by striking the
			 last sentence;</text>
					</subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
