          <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:203/ss:e">subsection (e)</cato:entity-ref>,
			 by redesignating such subsection as <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:203/ss:c" proposed="true">subsection (c)</cato:entity-ref>, and by striking
			 <quote>
              <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:203/ss:c,d">subsections (c) and (d)</cato:entity-ref>
